    ["Hide the bar text until you mouse over the frame. Keeps the tracker visually clean between pulls."] = "在你将鼠标移到框体上之前隐藏条文本。让追踪器在拉怪间保持视觉整洁。",
    ["Hide the bar when no prey hunt is active. Turn off to keep a placeholder bar visible at all times."] = "在没有猎物狩猎活动时隐藏该条。关闭则始终显示占位条。",
    ["Hide the bar whenever you leave the zone the current prey belongs to."] = "当你离开当前猎物所属区域时隐藏该条。",
    ["Hide the border drawn around each spell icon."] = "隐藏每个法术图标周围绘制的边框。",
