    ["Hide the border on this skin entirely. Only takes effect when the override above is enabled."] = "完全隐藏此皮肤上的边框。仅在启用上方覆盖时生效。",
    ["Hide the border outline entirely."] = "完全隐藏边框轮廓。",
    ["Hide the buff frame entirely, even when hovering its anchor area."] = "完全隐藏增益框体，即使悬停其锚定区域也不显示。",
    ["Hide the clockwise cooldown swipe animation drawn over %1$s icons. Duration text still works if it is enabled below."] = "隐藏绘制在 %1$s 图标上的顺时针冷却划扫动画。若下方启用了持续时间文本，它仍可正常显示。",
    ["Hide the combat timer outside of boss encounters, M+ dungeons, and PvP matches. Off shows the timer on every pull."] = "仅在首领战斗、大秘境和 PvP 对战之外隐藏战斗计时器。关闭后会在每次拉怪时显示计时器。",
    ["Hide the compact raid frame manager widget that lets you pick built-in raid profiles."] = "隐藏让你选择内置团队配置文件的紧凑团队框体管理器小部件。",
    ["Hide the cooldown swipe animation drawn over icons."] = "隐藏绘制在图标上的冷却划扫动画。",
