    ["Hide the default Blizzard prey indicator so only the QUI tracker is shown."] = "隐藏默认 Blizzard 猎物指示器，只显示 QUI 跟踪器。",
    ["Hide the display while in the open world. Useful if you only care about raid buffs inside instances."] = "在开放世界中隐藏显示。如果你只关心副本中的团队增益，这很有用。",
    ["Hide the drawer toggle button until you mouse over the minimap."] = "在你将鼠标移到小地图上方之前隐藏抽屉切换按钮。",
    ["Hide the duration and spell-name text on every bar in this container."] = "隐藏此容器中每条上的持续时间和法术名称文本。",
    ["Hide the duration countdown text on every icon in this row. The swipe animation still plays."] = "隐藏此行每个图标上的持续时间倒计时文本。划扫动画仍会播放。",
