    ["Hide this HUD element while you are riding a vehicle, overriding any Show rules above."] = "在你乘坐载具时隐藏此 HUD 元素，覆盖上方任何显示规则。",
    ["Hide this addon button from both the minimap and the drawer. Useful for buttons you never click."] = "将此插件按钮从小地图和抽屉中都隐藏。适合你从不点击的按钮。",
    ["Hide this chat frame's button bar while you are in combat, then restore it after combat ends."] = "在你战斗中隐藏此聊天框的按钮栏，战斗结束后再恢复。",
    ["Hide this frame whenever its anchor target is hidden, so dependent frames disappear together with the thing they follow."] = "当其锚点目标被隐藏时隐藏此框体，使依赖框体与其所跟随对象一起消失。",
    ["Hide this spell entirely from the CDM viewer. Useful for spells tracked automatically by the spec ruleset that you don't personally care about."] = "将此法术完全从 CDM 查看器中隐藏。适用于由专精规则集自动跟踪、但你个人不关心的法术。",
    ["Hide this widget's inline icon and keep the text. Not applied to icon-only widgets (Micro Menu, Travel) — hiding their icon would blank them."] = "隐藏此小部件的内联图标并保留文本。不适用于仅图标小部件（Micro 菜单、Travel） - 隐藏其图标会导致其空白。",
    ["Hide this widget's text and keep only its icon. Text-only widgets (FPS, Gold, …) become blank."] = "隐藏此挂件的文本，仅保留其图标。纯文本挂件（FPS、金币、…）将变为空白。",
    ["Hide this window without deleting it. The window keeps its layout and overrides and reappears when toggled back on."] = "隐藏此窗口而不删除它。窗口会保留其布局和覆盖，并在再次切换时重新出现。",
    ["Hides Blizzard tutorial popups, micro-button glows, and collection toasts."] = "隐藏 Blizzard 教程弹窗、小按钮闪光和收集吐司。",
