    ["QUI chat display, windows, and whisper tabs."] = "QUI 聊天显示、窗口和密语标签。",
    ["QUI conflicts with another addon"] = "QUI 与另一个插件冲突",
    ["QUI includes many small quality-of-life improvements: auto-repair, auto-sell junk, improved tooltips, chat enhancements, a crosshair overlay, skyriding helpers, and more."] = "QUI 包含许多小型质量提升：自动修理、自动出售垃圾、改进工具提示、聊天增强、准星覆盖层、驭空辅助等。",
    ["QUI is a full UI suite built around QUI 3 systems: custom unit and group frames, Cooldown Manager viewers, action bar styling, anchoring and layout tools, profile import/export, skinning, and quality-of-life modules - all configurable from one options panel."] = "QUI 是一个完整的 UI 套件，围绕 QUI 3 系统构建：自定义单位和队伍框架、Cooldown Manager 查看器、动作条样式、锚定和布局工具、配置导入/导出、皮肤，以及质量提升模块 - 所有内容都可在一个选项面板中配置。",
    ["QUI is designed to work alongside other addons, but conflicts can occur with addons that modify the same frames. Try disabling the conflicting addon to isolate the issue, then report it on GitHub with both addon names."] = "QUI 旨在与其他插件协同工作，但修改相同框架的插件可能会产生冲突。请尝试禁用冲突插件以隔离问题，然后连同两个插件名称一起在 GitHub 上报告。",
    ["QUI options (/qui)"] = "QUI 选项（/qui）",
    ["QUI replaces the default player, target, focus, party, and raid frames with custom-styled versions. Each unit type can be configured independently with health/power bars, name text, portraits, and aura displays."] = "QUI 会用自定义样式版本替换默认的玩家、目标、焦点、队伍和团队框架。每种单位类型都可独立配置，包含生命/能量条、名称文本、头像和光环显示。",
    ["QUI skins many Blizzard frames to match the addon's visual style. The autohide system lets you hide specific UI elements (like gryphons, XP bar, or micro menu) to clean up your screen."] = "QUI 会对许多 Blizzard 框架进行皮肤处理，使其符合插件的视觉风格。自动隐藏系统可隐藏特定 UI 元素（如狮鹫、经验条或微型菜单），让界面更整洁。",
    ["QUI styles and customizes your action bars with consistent appearance, keybind text, and optional per-bar overrides for size, spacing, and visibility."] = "QUI 会用一致的外观、按键绑定文本，以及可选的按条大小、间距和可见性覆盖，来样式化并自定义你的动作条。",
    ["QUI styles the minimap with custom borders and shape options, and provides data text panels that display useful information like FPS, latency, gold, and more."] = "QUI 会用自定义边框和形状选项重塑小地图，并提供数据文字面板，显示 FPS、延迟、金币等有用信息。",
    ["QUI's bag takeover. Mirrors the Bags row on the Module Addons page: enabling loads the module (live when possible), disabling hands bags back to Blizzard — a UI reload is prompted for a clean handoff. Everything below applies live while the module is enabled."] = "QUI 的背包接管。对应模块附加组件页面的 Bags 行：启用时加载该模块（如可能则实时生效），禁用时将背包交还给 Blizzard - 为了干净切换会提示重新加载界面。以下所有设置在模块启用时都会实时生效。",
    ["QUI's chat takeover. Enabled: chat is captured and rendered in QUI's own display. Disabled: QUI leaves chat completely stock."] = "QUI 的聊天接管。启用：聊天被捕获并渲染在 QUI 自己的显示中。禁用：QUI 完全保持原生聊天。",
