    ["Show a 3D unit portrait next to this frame. Side, size, gap, and border style are set below."] = "在该框体旁显示 3D 单位头像。侧边、尺寸、间距和边框样式在下方设置。",
    ["Show a Sell Junk button in the bag window while a merchant is open."] = "商人打开时，在背包窗口显示“出售垃圾”按钮。",
    ["Show a Whirling Surge cooldown icon on the skyriding bar."] = "在空中滑翔条上显示旋涡冲击冷却图标。",
    ["Show a brief explanation of each setting when you hover over it in this panel."] = "在此面板中悬停每个设置时，显示简短说明。",
    ["Show a bright edge on the active recharge slice for spells with charges."] = "为有充能的法术显示充能中的激活重充能切片边缘。",
    ["Show a bright spark at the leading edge of the filled portion of the bar."] = "在条形填充部分前缘显示明亮闪光。",
    ["Show a classification icon next to elite, rare, rare-elite, and boss NPCs on this unit frame."] = "在此单位框体上为精英、稀有、稀有精英和首领 NPC 显示分类图标。",
    ["Show a clickable Great Vault shortcut anchored relative to the minimap."] = "显示一个可点击的大秘境宝库快捷方式，锚定相对小地图的位置。",
    ["Show a colored border around the rotation assist icon."] = "为旋转辅助图标显示彩色边框。",
    ["Show a consumables window listing food, flasks, weapon enchants, runes, and healthstones based on the triggers below."] = "显示一个消耗品窗口，按下方触发条件列出食物、合剂、武器附魔、符文和治疗石。",
    ["Show a count next to each missing buff indicating how many group members are missing it."] = "在每个缺失增益旁显示计数，表示有多少队伍成员缺少它。",
    ["Show a crown icon on the party/raid leader and a flag icon on raid assistants."] = "在队伍/团队领袖上显示皇冠图标，在团队助理上显示旗帜图标。",
    ["Show a customizable reticle at the center of your screen for aiming and combat feedback."] = "在屏幕中心显示可自定义准星，用于瞄准和战斗反馈。",
    ["Show a dedicated icon strip for active defensive cooldowns on this frame."] = "在此框体上显示专用防御冷却图标条。",
    ["Show a draggable preview frame so you can position the distance bracket display."] = "显示一个可拖动的预览框体，以便定位距离分区显示。",
    ["Show a footer row on the bag window with the currencies enabled below."] = "在背包窗口底部显示一行，列出下方启用的货币。",
    ["Show a list of available hunts when you interact with a hunt table NPC, so you can pick the best prey at a glance."] = "与狩猎台 NPC 交互时显示可用狩猎列表，方便一眼选出最佳猎物。",
    ["Show a per-slot item level number on each piece of gear in the inspect window."] = "在检视窗口中为每件装备显示每个部位的物品等级数值。",
    ["Show a portrait next to each frame."] = "在每个框体旁显示头像。",
    ["Show a power bar below the health bar on this frame."] = "在此框体上的生命值条下方显示能量条。",
    ["Show a quality indicator on profession items placed on action bars."] = "在动作条上的专业物品上显示品质指示器。",
    ["Show a small durability bar on each slot overlay that has durability damage."] = "在有耐久度损伤的槽位叠加层上显示小耐久度条。",
    ["Show a small gear icon on items that belong to a saved equipment set (live bag and bank views)."] = "在属于已保存装备套装的物品上显示一个小齿轮图标（背包与银行视图）。",
    ["Show a text label on the player frame naming your current stance, shapeshift form, or aura."] = "在玩家框体上显示一个文本标签，标明当前姿态、变形形态或光环。",
    ["Show a tooltip line for attackable enemies that do not contribute forces."] = "为不会提供势力值的可攻击敌人显示一行提示信息。",
    ["Show a tooltip with class color, total, per-second, and percent when hovering a row."] = "悬停某一行时，显示带有职业颜色、总量、每秒和百分比的提示。",
    ["Show an alert when the prey enters an ambushable state so you can position for the takedown."] = "当猎物进入可伏击状态时显示警报，以便你为击杀做好站位。",
    ["Show an icon for the active stance/form next to the text."] = "在文本旁显示当前姿态/形态图标。",
    ["Show average equipped item level on player tooltips. Remote players may populate after a short inspect delay."] = "在玩家提示中显示已装备物品等级平均值。远程玩家可能会在短暂检视延迟后填充。",
    ["Show bar border"] = "显示条边框",
    ["Show bar text"] = "显示条文本",
    ["Show buffs Blizzard's raid frames would show."] = "显示 Blizzard 团队框体会显示的增益。",
    ["Show button bar for this frame"] = "显示此框体的按钮条",
    ["Show colored gem dots indicating how many gem slots the item has and whether each is filled."] = "显示彩色宝石点，指示物品宝石槽数量及是否已填充。",
    ["Show companion frames for pets alongside the main group."] = "在主队伍旁显示宠物伙伴框体。",
    ["Show debuffs Blizzard's raid frames would show."] = "显示 Blizzard 团队框体会显示的减益。",
    ["Show each visible enemy's forces contribution next to its nameplate."] = "在每个可见敌人的姓名板旁显示其势力贡献。",
    ["Show how many of an item you own across characters, bank, mail, and more on item tooltips. 'While Shift Held' shows the counts only while Shift is down."] = "在物品提示中显示你在角色、银行、邮件等处拥有该物品的总数。“按住 Shift 时”只会在按住 Shift 时显示计数。",
    ["Show item level and enchant overlays on inspected players. Requires a reload to take effect."] = "在检视玩家时显示物品等级和附魔覆盖层。需要重载后生效。",
    ["Show keybind overlays on action buttons"] = "在动作按钮上显示按键绑定覆盖层",
    ["Show numeric vigor count on the bar."] = "在条上显示数值形式的精力层数。",
    ["Show on Hover"] = "悬停时显示",
    ["Show on Melee Swings"] = "近战挥击时显示",
    ["Show only big-defensive buffs (Aspect of the Turtle, Divine Shield, Ice Block, etc.). Patch 12.0.1+."] = "仅显示大型减伤增益（龟壳、圣盾术、寒冰屏障等）。适用于 12.0.1+。",
    ["Show only buffs flagged as raid-relevant for your class — typically the ones you'd track on a raid frame."] = "仅显示标记为与你职业相关的团队增益 - 通常是你会在团队框体上追踪的那些。",
    ["Show only buffs that cannot be cancelled — flasks, food, world buffs, gear procs, and similar. Mutually exclusive with Only Cancellable."] = "仅显示不能取消的增益 - 合剂、食物、世界增益、装备触发等。与“仅可取消”互斥。",
    ["Show only buffs you applied yourself. Hides everything cast on you by others."] = "仅显示由你自己施放的增益。隐藏他人施放在你身上的所有内容。",
    ["Show only buffs you applied."] = "仅显示你施放的增益。",
    ["Show only buffs you can right-click off."] = "仅显示你可以右键移除的增益。",
    ["Show only buffs you can right-click to cancel. Excludes most consumables, talents, and gear procs. Mutually exclusive with Only Persistent."] = "仅显示你可以右键取消的增益。排除大多数消耗品、天赋和装备触发。与“仅持久”互斥。",
    ["Show only buffs you cannot right-click off."] = "仅显示你不能右键移除的增益。",
    ["Show only crowd-control effects (stuns, fears, roots, etc.). Patch 12.0.1+."] = "仅显示控制效果（昏迷、恐惧、缠绕等）。适用于 12.0.1+。",
    ["Show only debuffs flagged as raid-relevant — typically what raid frames would surface."] = "仅显示标记为团队相关的减益 - 通常是团队框体会显示的内容。",
    ["Show only debuffs whose dispel type your class can remove. Patch 12.0.1+."] = "仅显示你职业可以驱散类型的减益。适用于 12.0.1+。",
    ["Show only debuffs you applied — useful for DoT trackers and similar."] = "仅显示你施放的减益 - 对 DoT 追踪等很有用。",
    ["Show only debuffs you applied."] = "仅显示你施放的减益。",
    ["Show only spells flagged as important by C_Spell.IsSpellImportant. Patch 12.0.1+."] = "仅显示被 C_Spell.IsSpellImportant 标记为重要的法术。适用于 12.0.1+。",
    ["Show only while the buff is active. Hides the cooldown phase entirely."] = "仅在增益激活时显示。完全隐藏冷却阶段。",
    ["Show or hide the bag bar. Stays in sync with this element's enable toggle in Layout Mode."] = "显示或隐藏背包栏。与布局模式中该元素的启用开关保持同步。",
    ["Show or hide the micro menu. Stays in sync with this element's enable toggle in Layout Mode."] = "显示或隐藏微型菜单。与布局模式中该元素的启用开关保持同步。",
    ["Show or hide this action bar. Bars 2-8 can be individually disabled without affecting the pet or stance bars."] = "显示或隐藏此动作条。2-8号动作条可单独禁用而不影响宠物或姿态条。",
    ["Show per-enemy forces contribution on M+ tooltips and nameplates."] = "在 M+ 提示和姓名板上显示每个敌人的势力贡献。",
    ["Show realm names"] = "显示服务器名",
