    ["Thalassian Resistance (Vers)"] = "塔拉萨抗性（全能）",
    ["The CDM swipe overlay shows remaining cooldown time visually on each icon."] = "CDM 擦除覆盖层会在每个图标上以可视方式显示剩余冷却时间。",
    ["The Cooldown Manager displays your ability cooldowns as icon bars near your character. It integrates with Blizzard's CooldownViewer system and adds custom tracking, glow effects, and swipe overlays."] = "冷却管理器会在角色附近以图标条形式显示你的技能冷却。它与 Blizzard 的 CooldownViewer 系统集成，并添加自定义追踪、闪光效果和擦除覆盖层。",
    ["The Cooldown Manager icons aren't appearing"] = "冷却管理器图标没有出现",
    ["The Cooldown Manager powers QUI's essential and utility cooldown viewers, buff trackers, and tracked bars. Use |cff60A5FA/qui cdm|r to open the CDM Spell Composer and control what gets tracked, then use the Cooldown Manager tab for appearance, glows, keybind text, and custom-entry behavior. If you need Blizzard's viewer settings panel itself, use |cff60A5FA/cdm|r."] = "冷却管理器驱动 QUI 的核心与实用冷却查看器、增益追踪器和追踪条。使用 |cff60A5FA/qui cdm|r 打开 CDM 法术编辑器并控制追踪内容，然后在冷却管理器标签页中设置外观、闪光、按键文本和自定义条目行为。如果你需要 Blizzard 自己的查看器设置面板，请使用 |cff60A5FA/cdm|r。",
    ["The Datatexts module addon is disabled — enable it under Modules to configure datatexts. The Info Bar's widget lists below are empty until it loads."] = "数据文本模块插件已禁用 - 请在“模块”下启用它以配置数据文本。信息条下方的小组件列表在加载前为空。",
    ["The Datatexts module addon is disabled — enable it under Modules to configure datatexts. The datatext dropdowns below are empty until it loads."] = "数据文本模块插件已禁用 - 请在“模块”下启用它以配置数据文本。下方的数据文本下拉菜单在加载前为空。",
    ["The HUD Visibility section controls which elements show in and out of combat."] = "HUD 可见性部分控制哪些元素在战斗内外显示。",
    ["The anchoring system lets you position QUI elements relative to each other or to screen anchor points. This provides pixel-perfect control over your UI layout without needing Blizzard Edit Mode."] = "锚定系统可让你将 QUI 元素彼此相对或相对屏幕锚点定位。这提供了对界面布局的像素级精确控制，无需 Blizzard 编辑模式。",
    ["The combat timer shows elapsed encounter time during boss fights."] = "战斗计时器在首领战中显示已进行的战斗时间。",
