    ["Welcome"] = "欢迎",
    ["Welcome to QUI"] = "欢迎使用 QUI",
    ["What happens to bars when the tracked buff is not active: always show, fade to the alpha below, or hide entirely."] = "当追踪的增益未激活时，条的显示方式：始终显示、淡出到下方透明度，或完全隐藏。",
    ["What is QUI Layout Mode?"] = "什么是 QUI 布局模式？",
    ["What is QUI?"] = "什么是 QUI？",
    ["What is the Cooldown Manager (CDM)?"] = "什么是冷却管理器（CDM）？",
    ["What the Alts datatext shows on the bar: total gold across your tracked alts, or the number of tracked alts. The tooltip always lists every alt."] = "栏上的 Alts 数据文字显示什么：你追踪的角色总金币，或追踪角色数量。提示总会列出所有角色。",
    ["What the Alts datatext shows on the bar: total gold across your tracked alts, or the number of tracked alts. The tooltip always lists every alt. Applies everywhere the Alts datatext is shown, including datatext panels."] = "栏上的 Alts 数据文字显示什么：你追踪的角色总金币，或追踪角色数量。提示总会列出所有角色。适用于 Alts 数据文字出现的所有位置，包括数据文字面板。",
    ["What the alert is anchored to: the screen, the CDM Essential bar, or your focus unit frame."] = "警报锚定到什么：屏幕、CDM 关键条，或你的焦点单位框体。",
    ["What this binding does: cast a spell or macro, change target/focus/assist, open the unit menu, or send a ping. Spell and Macro reveal an input below for the spell name or macro body."] = "此绑定的作用：施放法术或宏、切换目标/焦点/协助、打开单位菜单，或发送标记。法术和宏会在下方显示输入框用于法术名或宏体。",
    ["What's New"] = "最新动态",
    ["When Blizzard would open a whisper in a new window (right-click popout, or the 'open whispers in a new window' setting), open a QUI conversation tab instead."] = "当 Blizzard 会在新窗口中打开密语时（右键弹出，或“在新窗口中打开密语”设置），改为打开一个 QUI 对话标签。",
    ["When ON (default), Healing Done / HPS sum each source's healing AND absorb shields. Turn off for pure HealingDone (matching Blizzard's stock meter)."] = "开启时（默认），Healing Done / HPS 会把每个来源的治疗量和吸收盾都计入。关闭则仅显示纯 HealingDone（与 Blizzard 原版计量表一致）。",
    ["When ON (default), clear all damage-meter sessions when a Mythic+ key starts so Overall begins at zero for that run."] = "开启时（默认），在史诗钥石开始时清空所有伤害统计会话，这样该次运行的 Overall 从零开始。",
    ["When ON (default), hide realm names: show \"Name\" instead of \"Name-Realm\" for cross-realm players on rows, tooltips, and the breakdown popup."] = "开启时（默认），隐藏位面名：跨服玩家在行、提示和分解弹窗中显示为“名字”而不是“名字-服务器”。",
    ["When ON (default), rows show the other metric in parentheses — e.g. DPS mode shows 1.5M (42.3M). Turn off to show only the primary value."] = "开启时（默认），行会在另一项指标后用括号显示，例如 DPS 模式显示 1.5M (42.3M)。关闭则只显示主数值。",
    ["When ON, windows showing Overall switch to Current when a key starts, then Current switches back to Overall when the key completes."] = "当 Overall 窗口可见时，在钥石开始后切换为 Current；钥石完成后 Current 再切回 Overall。",
    ["When Swap to Primary Position is active, also hide the primary power bar so both resources aren't shown together."] = "当启用“切换到主位置”时，也隐藏主能量条，这样不会同时显示两种资源。",
    ["When an NPC gossip has a single option, pick it automatically so you skip the popup."] = "当 NPC 闲聊只有一个选项时，自动选择它，跳过弹窗。",
    ["When an external button-skinning addon is installed, let it skin QUI's action buttons instead of QUI's built-in skin."] = "安装外部按钮皮肤插件时，让其为QUI动作按钮应用皮肤而非QUI内置皮肤。",
    ["When an external button-skinning addon is installed, let it skin buff/debuff icons instead of QUI's own border."] = "安装外部按钮皮肤插件时，让其为增益/减益图标应用皮肤而非QUI自有边框。",
    ["When an external button-skinning addon is installed, let it skin group-frame aura icons instead of QUI's own border."] = "安装外部按钮皮肤插件时，让其为队伍框架光环图标应用皮肤而非QUI自有边框。",
    ["When bars appear: always, only while the tracked buff/debuff is active, or only while in combat."] = "条何时出现：始终显示、仅在追踪的增益/减益激活时，或仅在战斗中。",
    ["When class color is off, use QUI accent color. Otherwise the custom Bar Color below is used."] = "当关闭职业色时，使用 QUI 强调色。否则使用下面自定义的条颜色。",
    ["When enabled, the macro selections below are stored per-character instead of being shared by every character on this AceDB profile. The toggle itself is always per-character. Turning it on copies your current profile selections as a starting point."] = "启用后，下面的宏选择将按角色分别保存，而不是在此 AceDB 配置中由所有角色共享。该开关本身始终按角色保存。开启时会复制你当前配置的选择作为起点。",
    ["When hovering a dead unit, any spell binding is temporarily replaced by your class's resurrection spell if you know one. Restores the original spell when the unit is alive."] = "悬停在死亡单位上时，任何法术绑定会临时替换为你职业的复活法术（如果你已学会）。单位复活后恢复原法术。",
    ["When icons appear: always visible, only while the spell is active/on cooldown, or only while in combat."] = "图标何时出现：始终可见、仅在法术激活/冷却中，或仅在战斗中。",
    ["When icons appear: always, only when the buff is active, or only while in combat."] = "图标何时出现：始终显示、仅当增益激活时，或仅在战斗中。",
    ["When on, %s messages use the days slider on the right instead of the default retention. When off, the default applies."] = "开启时，%s 消息使用右侧的天数滑条而不是默认保留时长。关闭时使用默认值。",
    ["When on, dragging only works while holding the move modifier. When off, any plain left-click drag repositions supported windows."] = "开启时，仅在按住移动修饰键时才能拖动。关闭时，任意普通左键拖拽都可移动受支持的窗口。",
    ["When recalling a message with Up/Down, also restore its original chat type (Say, Yell, Whisper target, channel) so pressing Enter sends to the same destination."] = "用上下方向键回溯消息时，也恢复其原始聊天类型（说、喊、密语目标、频道），这样按 Enter 会发送到相同目标。",
    ["When remaining duration drops below this, the bar switches to the Low-Time Color."] = "当剩余持续时间低于此值时，条会切换为低时间颜色。",
    ["When the anchor target is hidden but this frame stays visible, keep it at its last screen position instead of snapping toward the hidden anchor."] = "当锚点目标隐藏但此框体仍可见时，保持在上一次的屏幕位置，而不是朝向隐藏的锚点吸附。",
    ["When the native meter is visible. Always = shown at all times; In Combat = only during combat; Hidden = meter exists but is invisible."] = "当原生计量表可见时。始终 = 一直显示；战斗中 = 仅在战斗中；隐藏 = 计量表存在但不可见。",
    ["When the primary power bar is visible (always, in combat only, when depleted, etc.)."] = "当主能量条可见时（始终、仅战斗中、耗尽时等）。",
    ["When the secondary power bar is visible (always, in combat only, when depleted, etc.)."] = "当副能量条可见时（始终、仅战斗中、耗尽时等）。",
    ["When the secondary resource is dominant for your spec, swap it into the primary bar's position for that spec."] = "当副资源对你的专精是主资源时，将其切换到主条的位置。",
    ["When the skyriding bar is shown: always on, only while flying, or auto-fade out shortly after you land."] = "当天空骑行条显示时：始终开启、仅在飞行时，或在落地后自动淡出。",
    ["When to show the icon: always visible, only in combat, or only when you have a hostile target."] = "何时显示图标：始终可见、仅在战斗中，或仅当你有敌对目标时。",
    ["When to show tooltips for items in your bags and equipment. Modifier options only show the tooltip while the key is held."] = "何时显示背包和装备中物品的提示。修饰键选项只在按住按键时显示提示。",
    ["When to show tooltips for spells and abilities. Modifier options only show the tooltip while the key is held."] = "何时显示法术和技能的提示。修饰键选项只在按住按键时显示提示。",
    ["When to show tooltips for units (NPCs and players). Modifier options only show the tooltip while the key is held."] = "何时显示单位（NPC 和玩家）的提示。修饰键选项只在按住按键时显示提示。",
    ["When to show tooltips on QUI Cooldown Manager icons."] = "何时在 QUI 冷却管理器图标上显示提示。",
    ["When to show tooltips on QUI custom item/spell trackers."] = "何时在 QUI 自定义物品/法术追踪器上显示提示。",
    ["When to show tooltips on UI frames (action bars, unit frames, etc.)."] = "何时在 UI 框体上显示提示（动作条、单位框体等）。",
    ["When your character name contains a space (e.g., 'Foo Bar'), trigger on the first part. Most player names don't have spaces."] = "当你的角色名包含空格时（例如“Foo Bar”），对第一部分触发。大多数玩家名字不含空格。",
    ["Where global skin borders get their color: Theme (follows your theme accent), Class (your class color), or Custom (the color picker)."] = "全局皮肤边框的颜色来源：主题（跟随主题强调色）、职业（你的职业色）或自定义（颜色选择器）。",
    ["Where on the frame the %1$s indicator is anchored. X/Y Offset below nudges it from this anchor point."] = "%1$s 指示器在框体上的锚点。下面的 X/Y 偏移会将其从该点微调。",
    ["Where on the frame the bar is anchored."] = "条在框体上的锚点位置。",
    ["Where on the frame the classification icon is anchored."] = "分类图标在框体上的锚点位置。",
    ["Where on the frame the defensive icon strip is anchored. X/Y Offset below nudges it from this anchor point."] = "防御图标条在框体上的锚点位置。下面的 X/Y 偏移会将其从该点微调。",
    ["Where on the frame the first private aura icon is anchored. X/Y Offset below nudges it from this anchor point."] = "第一个私有灵气图标在框体上的锚点位置。下面的 X/Y 偏移会将其从该点微调。",
