    ["Where on the frame the raid target icon is anchored."] = "团队标记图标在框体上的锚点位置。",
    ["Where on the frame the role icon is anchored. X/Y Offset below nudges it from this anchor point."] = "职责图标在框体上的锚点位置。下面的 X/Y 偏移会将其从该点微调。",
    ["Where on the frame the square is anchored."] = "方块在框体上的锚点位置。",
