    ["Where the tick timings come from. Auto tries QUI's static table first, then live calibration."] = "刻度时间的来源。自动会先尝试 QUI 的静态表，然后进行实时校准。",
    ["Where tick marks are drawn. Thirds matches prey stages; Quarters is purely visual."] = "刻度线的绘制位置。Threeirds 适用于猎物阶段；Quarters 纯属视觉效果。",
    ["Whether the Time datatext shows your local system time or realm server time."] = "Time 数据文字显示本地系统时间还是服务器时间。",
    ["Whether the bar drains horizontally or vertically as the aura ticks down."] = "条在灵气倒计时时是水平还是垂直消耗。",
    ["Whether the detail rows stack above or below the bar. Auto picks based on where the frame is anchored on screen."] = "详情行是在条上方还是下方堆叠。自动会根据框体在屏幕上的锚定位置决定。",
    ["Whether this binding fires on a mouse button (including scroll) or on a keyboard key pressed while hovering a unit frame."] = "此绑定是在鼠标按键（含滚轮）上触发，还是在悬停单位框体时按下键盘按键触发。",
